[0.002, "o", "\u001b[1;20He for locale-ge\u001b[3;17Hes that are to be generated by the locale-ge\u001b[5;11He is of the\u001b[7;13He> <charse\u001b[9;6Here <locale> is one of the locales given in /usr/share/i18n/locale\u001b[10;14Het> is one of the character sets listed in /usr/share\u001b[12;6He locale-gen command will generate all the locale\u001b[13;14H\u001b[30m\u001b[103mem\u001b[m\u000f in /usr/lib/locale\u001b[15;21Hed locales is given in /usr/share\u001b[16;17Hed in this file. Uncomment the needed locales be\u001b[44;144H\u001b[0;10;7m\u000f3,14\u001b[45;4H\u001b[?25h"]
